rComments: His exam is very hard. But this is not why I gave him low rating. There is no problem with a hard exam. He shouldn't be course coordinator anymore. plz

Homework is optional, study the powerpoint slides for tests and quizzes; the average is around a D everytime, tests are extremely tough.  Theo is an entertainer.  He has a pretty cool accent that I joke about w/ people
Soogy is awesome.  Class is hard, but he does a good job and is hilarious.   OPA!
